target.comment: R4B `MeasureReport.implicitRules` maps as Equivalent to R5 `MeasureReport.implicitRules`

R4B `MeasureReport.improvementNotation` maps as Equivalent to R5 `MeasureReport.improvementNotation` - improvementNotation has compatible required binding for non-code type: http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/measure-improvement-notation|4.3.0 and http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/measure-improvement-notation|5.0.0 (Equivalent)
R4B `MeasureReport.language` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `MeasureReport.language` - language made the binding required (from Preferred) for http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/all-languages|5.0.0
R4B `MeasureReport.measure` maps as Equivalent to R5 `MeasureReport.measure`
R4B `MeasureReport.meta` maps as Equivalent to R5 `MeasureReport.meta`

R4B `MeasureReport.modifierExtension` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `MeasureReport.modifierExtension` - modifierExtension has change due to type change: R4B `modifierExtension` `Extension` maps as RelatedTo for R5 `modifierExtension`
R4B `MeasureReport.period` maps as Equivalent to R5 `MeasureReport.period`
R4B `MeasureReport.reporter` maps as RelatedTo to R5 `MeasureReport.reporter` - reporter has change due to type change: R4B `reporter` `Reference` maps as RelatedTo for R5 `reporter`

R4B `MeasureReport.status` maps as Equivalent to R5 `MeasureReport.status` - status has compatible required binding for code type: http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/measure-report-status|4.3.0 and http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/measure-report-status|5.0.0 (Equivalent)
